Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:02.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all started with the Sacred Tree.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:04.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fighting and searching\nfor our dreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:06.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a strong bond\nis formed between us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:07.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new hope!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bright future begins now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:13.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku who controls the huge pack\nof demon rats comes to a decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:14.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha rushes to help\nthe siblings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:17.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}who face a crisis after\na heart-wrenching reunion...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:19.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And who appears but Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:21.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final shard guides us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:22.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the other side of the well,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:23.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a new day awaits in\nthe age of warring states!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:25.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Feudal Fairytale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:26.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:04.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You let your subordinates\neat the meat of their prey,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:06.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and devour the bones yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:10.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are Zushinezumi....huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had a hankering for\nbones like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:22.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're quite skilled, Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:29.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bring that little shrine that\nhe has on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:31.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:35.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't make a mistake\nand open it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:37.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They keep coming, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:55.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rats will scatter everywhere\nand attack wherever humans live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everywhere is overrun by rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:05.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:07.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You said that Zushinezumi increase
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:08.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in proportion to the numbers\nwhich are cut, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:09.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:11.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They don't die even if\nyou cut them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:12.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so they keep increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:16.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since they've spread so far,\nwe can't trace the source.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:19.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By source, you mean\nthe miniature shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:20.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard that if you destroy\nthe shrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:23.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the rats will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's like they're headed\nfor one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:17.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Somewhere, there is a {\i1}mayose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:18.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mayose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:22.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A spell that lures demons together,\nthen destroys them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:25.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But only one with immense\nspiritual power can cast such a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only one capable of this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}is Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the end of this flow of rats\nis Kikyo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:40.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll try to go to the source,\nwhere the rats are coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:41.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:42.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It bothers {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That the number of rats\nhasn't decreased at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:49.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which means that the shrine\nis still letting rats out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:52.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So we must go to the source\nor it will not end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:55.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's split into two groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go with Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:00.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rats are climbing something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-It looks like a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It reaches up all the way\nto heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rats are disappearing\ninto the {\i1}sky....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:21.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this the {\i1}mayose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:29.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo has come out of hiding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:35.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do not close the doors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That bastard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was enjoying this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:44.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I close these doors,\nthe rats will stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:45.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may save some lives.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm being watched...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:56.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I close the doors,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:01.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku will know that my\nmemory has returned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:05.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:06.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Were you behind this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:14.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:18.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,On my way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I saw countless villages\ndevoured by rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:30.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How I wish you were not\na part of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:38.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I cannot....disobey my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:44.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:46.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mustn't, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:03.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Killing them will only\nresult in more rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, please take care\nof the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:06.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:13.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter what,\NI must destroy that shrine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:18.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They won't even\nturn to look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:20.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're intently heading\ntowards their destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:25.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which means the power\nof the{\i0} mayose {\i1}is enormous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:42.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amazing....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happens to the rats\nwho climb up to the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They probably become purified.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:50.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No sign of Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:06.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So she laid the trap\nand ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:08.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bothersome woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:23.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-Demon slugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:33.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just when I thought\NI had lured her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:34.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakudoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:37.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She left this silly tree\nand went into hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:40.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the one\nwho released the rats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:43.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Need you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The {\i1}mayose{\i0} tree\nis starting to rot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we leave it like that,\nit'll fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:58.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you slay us?\NMe and the demon slugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:08:59.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:00.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't use the Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:04.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you bring down the tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:06.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you'll be doing exactly\nwhat Hakudoshi wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know that, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He only realized it\nafter I told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In any case, I must\nprotect the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:19.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My arrow should be able to\nhandle a demon like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:23.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! That was great, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:24.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I have a large target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:27.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bastard, don't you move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you know how many villages\nwere devoured by rats
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:32.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,just to bring Kikyo out of hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:36.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Is that what's upsetting you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:40.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why bother with things that\ndon't involve you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:42.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well {\i1}then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:45.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,maybe I'll interfere with those villagers\nthere who are trying to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:47.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:51.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:54.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He used it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:55.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you see Kikyo,\ngive her a message:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:06.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as she keeps running\nfrom Naraku,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:09.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the same thing will happen\nover and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:21.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}K-Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:24.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- The rats are acting {\i1}strange....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:28.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until now, they were totally\nintent to getting to the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:32.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe the spiritual power\nof the tree is weakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:35.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must hurry and get rid\nof the demon slugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:36.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take care of the demons\nhigher up the tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:39.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:47.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are the rats going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:54.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:57.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:00.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't add to your crimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:02.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:13.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rats are returning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:19.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Zushinezumi are\nheaded this way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was the spell broken?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:25.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad. I can't suck in\nall of them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:34.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are just too many.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:36.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me the shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:42.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If that shrine is broken,\nthe rats will disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:43.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Remember, Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You....are{\i0} a Demon Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:51.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Saimyosho are watching me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I do anything that seems\nlike a betrayal to Naraku,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:56.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}that infant...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:59.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll never be able to get near\NNaraku's heart!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rats!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've destroyed all\nthe {\i1}slugs....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}bad....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:34.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rats aren't trying to\nclimb up the tree anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The tree must have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! They're coming after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:43.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if I kill them,\nthey multiply.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These rats are such a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:50.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:52.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Snap out of it and transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:53.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're getting outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:54.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're gonna run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The {\i1}mayose{\i0} tree won't help\nanymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:00.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go and\ndestroy that shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:00.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:09.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The rats have fallen out of\nformation and are scattering!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you fly any faster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- You're heavy, stupid!\N- Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:20.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:21.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Destroy the shrine!\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you understand, Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If nothing's done, you'll fall prey\nto the rats, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:34.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Naraku would probably\norder me to do this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:38.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To protect the shrine\neven if it means death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:40.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:43.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:46.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:51.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, get on Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The ground is too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:06.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:10.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:11.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:15.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damned box!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I break {\i1}it....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:22.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:28.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It won't break!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:30.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it being protected\nby a demonic barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:36.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry and get away, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:38.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:44.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:47.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Inuyasha!\N- I'm going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The smell of blood!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:53.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! I have a bad\nfeeling about this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:56.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The smell of this blood...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:57.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it Sango's?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:08.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The presence of\nthe Sacred Jewel shard...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:09.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:11.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:36.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! If I use my Wind Tunnel,\nit'll take Sango as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:40.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:42.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A sacred arrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demonic barrier is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry! Break the shrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:16.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The {\i1}rats....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:22.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, the rats are\ndisappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:24.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The shrine has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:52.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:04.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:09.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's badly hurt...\nall because of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:12.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:21.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:33.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:38.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:49.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:56.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Saimyosho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:07.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is that woman, Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:09.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did she protect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:11.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hakudoshi...\NSo you were watching me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to put her\nin harm's way anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:26.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must defeat Naraku\nas soon as possible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:31.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:36.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:46.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if Sango is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:07.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She was bitten badly\nby the rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:15.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Physically, she's probably okay.\NShe's pretty strong for a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,More than that, it's the shock\nshe received
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:20.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,learning that Kohaku had something\nto do with the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:25.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, are you in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:28.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I cannot forgive what\NKohaku did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:30.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because of those rats, many\nvillages were destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not only {\i1}that....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:49.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:01.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:04.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At the castle that was\nassaulted by the birds,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:06.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he killed many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:12.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! They weren't killed\nby the {\i1}birds....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if Naraku ordered it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:23.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,what Kohaku did\nis unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:25.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know that in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:30.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when Kohaku was attacked\nby the rats,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:33.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I felt as though my heart\nwas being crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:36.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I saw that he\nwas okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:39.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I felt relief from\nthe bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:44.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just can't hate Kohaku,\nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, that is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't have to force yourself\nto hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:52.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:54.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,even after {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:58.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you regret protecting Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:00.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:03.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But if I hadn't protected him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think I would be regretting\nit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:07.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:11.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is the way of\nthe human heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:13.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you, Miroku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:28.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:32.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You would stoop to all this\njust to lure me out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:45.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asuka.... Kocho....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this and fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:03.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will search for his whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:47.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After a long absence,\NI return to the present-day world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:49.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,where I face endless questions\nabout Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:52.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your boyfriend is at your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:53.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to see! I want to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:55.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your delinquent boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.99,0:24:00.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Inuyasha breaks the bike\nthat Mom gave to Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:02.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!\NI'll pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.50,0:24:03.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:05.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're going to use the Adamant Barrage\nto create diamonds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:09.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Lucky but Two-Timing Scoundrel!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.30,0:24:12.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm make a ton of 'em with Tetsusaiga!
